003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \n    id=\"codeblock-id-11\" \n    class=\"\n      chroma \n      !tw-block \n      tw-p-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003ehttp://localhost/wp-admin/admin.php?page=wc-admin\u0026amp;path=%2Fcustomize-store\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"tw-inline\" loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/xss1.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/xss1_hu_bb0707175c00f838.webp 800w, /2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/xss1_hu_1cc7839f3880b1dc.webp 1200w, /2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/xss1_hu_a4bb0fe57020bd51.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Sự kiện alert() khi postMessage từ console browser\" height=\"481\" width=\"1224\"\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eAn alert() event triggered when postMessage is sent from the browser console\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e👉 \u003ccode\u003ealert()\u003c/code\u003e is triggered. Using the browser debugger I checked which file \u003ccode\u003e5292.js\u003c/code\u003e was loaded from in the browser.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"tw-inline\" loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/debug1.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/debug1_hu_9a436ec5926c044.webp 800w, /2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/debug1_hu_6a88f3dfd66389e8.webp 1200w, /2025-10-10-cve-2025-5062/debug1_hu_f806f1b917112e91.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"5292.js từ debug của browser\" height=\"172\" width=\"1160\"\u003e\n\u003cem\u003e5292.js from browser debugger\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"sources--sinks\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#sources--sinks\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.3 Sources \u0026amp; Sinks\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSource\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ccode\u003eevent.data\u003c/code\u003e from \u003ccode\u003ewindow.postMessage\u003c/code\u003e (specifically \u003ccode\u003eevent.data.url\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSink\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ccode\u003ewindow.location.href = event.data.url\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"exploit\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#exploit\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e16 Exploit\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"proof-of-concept-poc\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#proof-of-concept-poc\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e16.1 Proof of Concept (PoC)\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreate a webpage with the following source:\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-closed show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.4