3e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003esanitize_text_field\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$_POST\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e[\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026#34;nonce\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e])\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003enull\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e👉 The patch adds an input filtering layer for the \u003ccode\u003enonce\u003c/code\u003e variable, ensuring data received from the request will have dangerous characters removed before further processing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff.png\" title=\"Diff — code change comparison between vulnerable and patched versions\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eCode change comparison between vulnerable and patched versions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eDiff — code change comparison between vulnerable and patched versions\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff_hu_e3b3dab6f4820d7b.webp 800w, /2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff_hu_2ee08b4a4113e03e.webp 1200w, /2025-10-07-cve-2025-6832/diff_hu_80eccaa43b35bf20.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Diff — code change comparison between vulnerable and patched versions\" height=\"132\" width=\"1768\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eCode change comparison between vulnerable and patched versions\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"vulnerable-code\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#vulnerable-code\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e12.2 Vulnerable code\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe vu