\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e        \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ereturn\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003efalse\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e    \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003epermission_check\u003c/code\u003e specifies that only users with at least \u003cstrong\u003econtributor\u003c/strong\u003e privileges can use this API.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe haven\u0026rsquo;t identified the exact \u003cstrong\u003enamespace\u003c/strong\u003e here because it is declared elsewhere in the source. We trace using the \u003ccode\u003esave_css\u003c/code\u003e route.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAccess \u003ccode\u003e/wp-json/\u003c/code\u003e and search for \u003ccode\u003esave_css\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search.png\" title=\"Search\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eSearch\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eSearch\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search_hu_6cbc6c1c13983205.webp 800w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search_hu_d4e7673ff0329c17.webp 1200w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/search_hu_a498f0e7fedce1e2.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Search\" height=\"451\" width=\"1557\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eSearch\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe results show the actual endpoint:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highli