.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/button\u003e\n        \n      \u003cbutton \n        class=\"\n          tw-select-none \n          tw-mx-2 \n          tw-block \n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \n          print:!tw-hidden\" \n        disabled\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \n    id=\"codeblock-id-32\" \n    class=\"\n      chroma \n      !tw-block \n      tw-p-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003ehttp://localhost/wp-json/woolentor/v1/save_css\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo find where this \u003cstrong\u003enamespace\u003c/strong\u003e is declared, search the source for \u003ccode\u003e'woolentor/v1'\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space.png\" title=\"Name Space\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eName Space\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eName Space\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space_hu_1253aa0c1786a6c.webp 800w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space_hu_cb1d2beb384dd270.webp 1200w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/name_space_hu_10bd82e751c8b23a.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Name Space\" height=\"423\" width=\"895\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eName Space\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere are multiple results, but since we\u0026rsquo;re analyzing the \u003cstrong\u003eREST API\u003c/strong\u003e feature, focus on the \u003cstrong\u003eApi.php\u003c/strong\u003e file.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003eregister_routes( $namespace )\u003c/code\u003e in \u003ccode\u003eManage_Styles\u003c/code\u003e requires the \u003ccode\u003e$namespace\u003c/code\u003e parameter, so \u003ccode\u003ewoolentor/v1\u003c/code\u003e is likely passed in by the class instantiation in Api.php. Search for \u003ccode\u003eManage_Styles\u003c/code\u003e in Api.php to confirm.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi.png\" title=\"Call Api\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eCall Api\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eCall Api\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi_hu_9d7b482082b2093d.webp 800w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi_hu_ebc46bd15ab6c20c.webp 1200w, /2025-10-05-cve-2025-58990/callapi_hu_c53e9b5db3aaac4.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Call Api\" height=\"337\" width=\"1509\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eCall Api\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe namespace is indeed called and passed that way.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e👉 Therefore, sending a \u003cstrong\u003ePOST\u003c/strong\u003e to \u003ccode\u003ehttp://localhost/wp-json/woolentor/v1/save_css\u003c/code\u003e will invoke the \u003ccode\u003esave_block_css\u003c/code\u003e callback to add/update block CSS in the file and database. When visiting a post whose \u003ccode\u003epost_id\u003c/code\u003e has saved block CSS, \u003ccode\u003egenerate_inline_css\u003c/code\u003e will retrieve the block CSS and inline it inside a \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;style type=\u0026quot;text/css\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/style\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e tag in the post.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"exploit\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#exploit\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e13 Exploit\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"detect-xss\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#detect-xss\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e13.1 Detect XSS\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse a user with the \u003cstrong\u003econtributor\u003c/strong\u003e role to create any post and note its ID.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSend a \u003cstrong\u003ePOST\u003c/strong\u003e request to \u003ccode\u003ehttp://localhost/wp-json/woolentor/v1/save_css\u003c/code\u003e with an XSS payload:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fo