"  alt=\"callstack 12\" height=\"282\" width=\"1262\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003ePayload merged into $clauses\\['where']\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13.png\" title=\"callstack 13\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eObserve last_query where SQL executes\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003ecallstack 13\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13_hu_5e7d40b0d96f116d.webp 800w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13_hu_fd85d1979310cefa.webp 1200w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/callstack13_hu_ea1f1f4e82fa11a7.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"callstack 13\" height=\"804\" width=\"1520\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eObserve last_query where SQL executes\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExecution Flow Diagram\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart.png\" title=\"chart\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eExecution flow of WP_Query leading to SQLi\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003echart\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart_hu_3259038ae9ccd716.webp 800w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart_hu_de02405b431cc4a7.webp 1200w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/chart_hu_a69045bd01b745df.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"chart\" height=\"1094\" width=\"2451\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eExecution flow of WP_Query leading to SQLi\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"exploit\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#exploit\" cla