03e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect.png\" title=\"Detect\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eResponse shows delay caused by payload execution\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eDetect\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect_hu_1c7d5def755e00b5.webp 800w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect_hu_2615643d2f4824a8.webp 1200w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/detect_hu_143da15c4570bda5.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Detect\" height=\"267\" width=\"433\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eResponse shows delay caused by payload execution\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"conclusion\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#conclusion\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e19 Conclusion\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eCVE-2022-21661\u003c/strong\u003e vulnerability in \u003cstrong\u003eWordPress Core\u003c/strong\u003e, prior to version \u003cstrong\u003e5.8.3\u003c/strong\u003e (affecting versions back to \u003cstrong\u003e3.7.37\u003c/strong\u003e), stems from improper \u003cstrong\u003esanitization\u003c/strong\u003e in \u003ccode\u003eWP_Query\u003c/code\u003e, leading to a potential SQL Injection vulnerability.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"references\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#references\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e20 References\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://portswigger.net/web-security/sql-injection/cheat-sheet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eSQL Injection cheat sheet - PortSwigger\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2022-21661\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eCVE-2022-21661 Detail\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"notes\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#notes\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e21 Notes\u003c/h2\u003e",
        "language": "en"
    },
