e.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \n    id=\"codeblock-id-8\" \n    class=\"\n      chroma \n      !tw-block \n      tw-p-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eSELECT\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e*\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eFROM\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003ewp_easy\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003equotes\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efamilies\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eWHERE\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efamily\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;Roboto\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eAND\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eSUBSTRING\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eDATABASE\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(),\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"mi\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"mi\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;w\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"conclusion\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#conclusion\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e4 Conclusion\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe vulnerability \u003cstrong\u003eCVE-2025-26943\u003c/strong\u003e in the WordPress \u003cstrong\u003eEasy Quotes\u003c/strong\u003e plugin (versions prior to \u003cstrong\u003e1.2.3\u003c/strong\u003e) is caused by concatenating user-supplied input directly into SQL queries instead of using prepared statements (\u003ccode\u003e$wpdb-\u0026gt;prepare\u003c/code\u003e), which results in SQL Injection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe official patch replaces string concatenation with \u003ccode\u003e$wpdb-\u0026gt;prepare\u003c/code\u003e, ensuring user input is safely handled.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey takeaways\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlways use \u003ccode\u003e$wpdb-\u0026gt;prepare()\u003c/code\u003e when interacting with the database in WordPress to prevent SQL Injection.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRegularly update plugins and perform security checks to avoid becoming an attack target.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"references\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#references\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e5 References\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://portswigger.net/web-security/sql-injection/cheat-sheet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eSQL Injection cheat sheet - PortSwigger\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://patchstack.com/database/wordpress/plugin/easy-quotes/vulnerability/wordpress-easy-quotes-plugin-1-2-2-sql-injection-vulnerability\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eWordPress Easy Quotes Plugin \u0026lt;= 1.2.2 is vulnerable to SQL Injection\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
        "language": "en"
    },
    {
        "title" : "CVE-2025-39569 Analysis \u0026 POC",
